casebody.data:
Stephanie PANTTI, Personal Representative of the Estate of Anthony Norczyk, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
KYLE DANEK, DDS, and Michigan Community Dental Clinics, Inc., d/b/a Marquette Community Dental Clinics, Defendants,
and
Nelson Gencheff, DO, and DLP Marquette General Hospital, LLC, d/b/a UP Health System-Marquette, Defendants-Appellants. SC: 158752
COA: 339713 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 2, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the October 16, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
